<FIRST>u f PM-WallStreet2pm     09-07 0302</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Wall Street 2pm,0318</SECOND>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The stock market staged a modest upswing today,
rebounding from Wednesday's broad decline.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials, which fell 24.89 points
on Wednesday, rose 3.61 to 2,723.40 by 2 p.m. today on Wall Street.
